<subSubSection pageId="70" pageNumber="828" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="70.[1453,2664,298,1234]" pageId="70" pageNumber="828">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1454,1688,808,837]" pageId="70" pageNumber="828">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Coppery Sprite is nocturnal. It is probably a canopy species. Mistnetted over a river in Lanjak Entimau and Samunsam wildlife sanctuaries (
<collectingCountry box="[2507,2629,847,876]" name="Malaysia" pageId="70" pageNumber="828">Sarawak</collectingCountry>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
