</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="70" pageNumber="828" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="70.[1453,2664,298,1234]" pageId="70" pageNumber="828">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1456,1808,930,955]" pageId="70" pageNumber="828">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List, as its area of occupancy is estimated to be less than 
<quantity box="[2012,2124,961,994]" metricMagnitude="6" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="70" pageNumber="828" unit="km" value="2000.0">2000 km</quantity>
?2. Less than 20 individuals have been captured at only eight locations in 
<collectingRegion box="[1940,2022,1001,1034]" country="Malaysia" name="Sabah" pageId="70" pageNumber="828">Sabah</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[2095,2210,1001,1034]" name="Malaysia" pageId="70" pageNumber="828">Sarawak</collectingCountry>
. Extent and quality of its habitat seem to be in continuous decline.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
